018-08-01T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ed286a8a45e8a74886de1770bd12daca2889b24","tid":763142,"uid":1518,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"Intel=on9"},{"pid":"22cacc64729df7811d090d359f909cc5dcabccc6","tid":763142,"uid":111639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"其實CPU漏洞只會越爆越多越大鑊<br />\n以前無人真係會走去研究CPU有無漏洞<br />\n直到之前連爆2鑊<br />\n成班Hacker先突然發現因為無人攻擊而疏於防範，班Intel Engineer個個都Hea慣哂<br />\n真係會隨時清Intel袋 咁多年來既漏洞比人挖返哂出來"},{"pid":"64d1943d84af6d6b68a8175c273bfa4ecda7d555","tid":763142,"uid":53466,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:42:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e150adadc162fd6bf6b549d004372fd791ba4a24","tid":763142,"uid":38891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"AMD Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db08ff6c468c958311e01c42ed178556584b1022","tid":763142,"uid":38891,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/204841_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F204841_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=ffa339f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c416af205acb467b424eb86bdebc9687a6439d","tid":763142,"uid":38891,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/205253_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F205253_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=a4c7f291&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6f46e5a311d38b2f378644c848454ed6c6de372","tid":763142,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"intel=tvb, 極速亞視化"},{"pid":"e91cef34dcb0b63c50ed3d5a36bfd87dfa129e24","tid":763142,"uid":67384,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:07:31.000Z","msg":"香港人，現實啲啦。<br />\n<br />\n你覺得佢哋care咩bug打咩漏洞？<br />\n<br />\n只要個bug唔會偷到佢bitcon電子銀包同google chrome個password list。<br />\n<br />\n就實有一堆人話：<br />\n1.怕咩呀<br />\n2.intel好超<br />\n3.intel比amd方便<br />\n4.amd都有bug啦<br />\n5.@#$%<br />\nto N<br />\n<br />\n只要唔死過人沙士，雷曼，蒙牛，鄰近地區產電子產品都有人相信過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇事嘅</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n冇事咪冇事囉，<br />\n講咩CPU 漏洞，<br />\n會care會自己跟進，<br />\n放上黎真係who FxxKing care?<br />\n<br />\n見到你都辛苦。"},{"pid":"252fee1cbb18b1c3f0a61a5f40391f07cedb2102","tid":763142,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"CPU界馬時亨<br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 明知有BUG都唔笑笑口懶理<br />\n家用機永不錄用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a604e0b0418d9989c3bebcf46c0e659febbbec35","tid":763142,"uid":97439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22cacc64729df7811d090d359f909cc5dcabccc6","tid":763142,"uid":111639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"其實CPU漏洞只會越爆越多越大鑊<br />\n以前無人真係會走去研究CPU有無漏洞<br />\n直到之前連爆2鑊<br />\n成班Hacker先突然發現因為無人攻擊而疏於防範，班Intel Engineer個個都Hea慣哂<br />\n真係會隨時清Intel袋 咁多年來既漏洞比人挖返哂出來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:58:46.000Z","msg":"放心啦唔會清袋<br />\n企業黎講用慣左唔會轉<br />\n<br />\n簡單例子 <br />\nlotus note 各種問題 落後唔方便<br />\n老公司同政府做到執笠果日都係用緊佢"}]}